1. *Bili* smo sretni što smo se vratili kući. (We were happy to be back home.)
2. On će *biti* tu uskoro. (He will be here soon.)
3. *Bila* sam umorna od putovanja. (I was tired from the trip.) 
4. Svi će *biti* tu za 15 minuta. (Everyone will be here in 15 minutes.)
5. Ona je *bila* tamo preko leta. (She was there over the summer.)
6. *Budite* spremni za putovanje. (Be prepared for the journey.)
7. *Bilo* je puno lepih trenutaka. (There were a lot of beautiful moments.)
8. Moraćeš da *budeš* spreman. (You will have to be ready.)